articles.title: Video: Skydiver Left Dangling Mid-Air As Parachute Caught On Aircraft Tail - NDTV
articles.description: Heart-stopping footage released Thursday by Australian authorities showed the moment a skydiver was left dangling thousands of metres in the air after their parachute caught on the plane's tail.
